PN,44101
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1774548358
OL,3,COne of Lyra McKee murder accused 'part
OL,4,Cof shooting party'
OL,6,FOne of the men accused of the murder
OL,7,Fof journalist Lyra McKee was "part of
OL,8,Fthe shooting party" and "stewarded"
OL,9,Fthe crowd, Belfast Crown Court has
OL,10,Fheard.
OL,12,FThe 29-year-old author died after
OL,13,Fbeing hit by a bullet as she stood
OL,14,Fclose to police vehicles while
OL,15,Fobserving the disturbances in the
OL,16,FCreggan area of Londonderry on April
OL,17,F18 2019.
OL,19,FIt came as TV presenter Reggie Yates
OL,20,Fand an MTV crew had been filming in
OL,21,Fthe area for a documentary.
OL,26,@oD@^OUpD@SO]pD@YOUpD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1774548358
OL,3,COne of Lyra McKee murder accused 'part
OL,4,Cof shooting party'
OL,6,FSeveral rounds of petrol bombs had
OL,7,Fbeen directed at police late on April
OL,8,F18, as well as a car being set on fire
OL,9,Fduring chaotic scenes which culminated
OL,10,Fin four shots being fired towards
OL,11,Fpolice, which the prosecution contend
OL,12,Fwere aimed and deliberate.
OL,14,FPeter Cavanagh, 37, of Mary Street in
OL,15,FDerry, is one of three charged with Ms
OL,16,FMcKee's murder.
OL,18,FThe prosecution has argued Cavanagh is
OL,19,F"person G" identified in footage by
OL,20,Fhis clothes, height and build.
OL,26,@{D@AOU{D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1774548358
OL,3,COne of Lyra McKee murder accused 'part
OL,4,Cof shooting party'
OL,6,FProsecuting barrister David McDowell
OL,7,FKC said a person identified as G in
OL,8,Fthe footage is wearing a camouflage
OL,9,Fmask, bomber jacket, skinny jeans and
OL,10,Fdark Nike trainers, is of a slim build
OL,11,Fand walks in an upright manner.
OL,13,FAs the court was shown mobile footage
OL,14,Fof the shooting, he contended Cavanagh
OL,15,Fis person G who is seen "walking
OL,16,Fbriskly" with the gunman, positioning
OL,17,Fhimself in the middle of the road, and
OL,18,Fturning to face the crowd twice, "as
OL,19,Fif stewarding them".
OL,26,@wD@YOUxD@HO]zD@bOU{D@SO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1774548358
OL,3,COne of Lyra McKee murder accused 'part
OL,4,Cof shooting party'
OL,6,FThe same person is also contended to
OL,7,Fbe seen moving towards the gunman "to
OL,8,Fassist" after the shots were fired
OL,9,Fwhere two other people were picking
OL,10,Fthings up, believed to be cartridges.
OL,12,F"Whenever he arrives at the scene, he
OL,13,Fis part of the shooting party... he is
OL,14,Fnot there accidentally, he is there
OL,15,Ffor a reason," he added.
OL,17,FJudge Patricia Smyth queried in what
OL,18,Fway G was stewarding the crowd.
OL,26,@oD@cOUpD@GO]tD@AOUwD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1774548358
OL,3,COne of Lyra McKee murder accused 'part
OL,4,Cof shooting party'
OL,6,FMr McDowell emphasised the "purpose"
OL,7,Fwith which he said that four people,
OL,8,Fidentified as B, C, D and G who
OL,9,Faccompanied the gunmen, walked.
OL,11,F"It is the purpose with which Cavanagh
OL,12,Fis walking shows he is part of the
OL,13,Fshooting party, and ultimately the
OL,14,Factions he takes," he said.
OL,16,F"If he was eating a curry chip he
OL,17,Fwould not be behaving (that way).
OL,19,F"He looks like he has a position of
OL,20,Fresponsibility."
OL,26,@nD@\OUnD@dO]sD@AOUvD@RO]xD@AOU{D@AOU|D@
OL,26,APO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1774548358
OL,3,COne of Lyra McKee murder accused 'part
OL,4,Cof shooting party'
OL,6,FThe trial also heard that Cavanagh's
OL,7,FDNA had been found on a zip pull found
OL,8,Fin "burning clothes".
OL,10,FIt is contended that zip pull had been
OL,11,Fon a jacket which Cavanagh was wearing
OL,12,Fon April 18.
OL,14,FCavanagh has not given evidence in
OL,15,Fresponse.
OL,17,FThe New IRA claimed responsibility for
OL,18,Fthe death of Ms McKee.
OL,26,@pD@DOUpD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
