OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1774548358
OL,3,COne of Lyra McKee murder accused 'part
OL,4,Cof shooting party'
OL,6,FJordan Gareth Devine, 25, of Bishop
OL,7,FStreet, and Paul McIntyre, 58, of
OL,8,FKells Walk ` have also been charged
OL,9,Fwith Ms McKee's murder.
OL,11,FThey are additionally facing other
OL,12,Fcharges connected to the shooting and
OL,13,Fthe rioting.
OL,15,FSix other Derry men are on trial on
OL,16,Fcharges including rioting and throwing
OL,17,Fpetrol bombs.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1774548358
OL,3,COne of Lyra McKee murder accused 'part
OL,4,Cof shooting party'
OL,6,FThey are: Joseph Patrick Barr, 37, of
OL,7,FSandringham Drive, Jude Forest Coffey,
OL,8,F28, of Gartan Square, Joseph Anthony
OL,9,FCampbell, 25, of Gosheden Cottages,
OL,10,FPatrick Anthony Gallagher, 33, of John
OL,11,FField Place, Christopher Joseph
OL,12,FGillen, 45, of Balbane Pass, and
OL,13,FKieran George McCool, 57, of
OL,14,FBallymagowan Gardens.
OL,16,FAnother man accused of rioting and
OL,17,Fthrowing petrol bombs on the night of
OL,18,Fthe murder died during trial
OL,19,Fproceedings last year.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1774548358
OL,3,COne of Lyra McKee murder accused 'part
OL,4,Cof shooting party'
OL,6,FIt is the prosecution's case that the
OL,7,Fthree men accused of murder had
OL,8,Faccompanied a lone gunman to the
OL,9,Ffiring point on the night, and had
OL,10,Fencouraged or assisted him.
OL,12,FThey have all denied the charges and
OL,13,Frefused to give evidence.
OL,15,FThe trial on Thursday was also shown
OL,16,Ffootage of the firing of four shots
OL,17,Ftowards police, after which screaming
OL,18,Fcan be heard.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1774548358
OL,3,COne of Lyra McKee murder accused 'part
OL,4,Cof shooting party'
OL,6,FMr McDowell contended they were "very
OL,7,Fmuch aimed shots", adding: "Not shots
OL,8,Ffired wildly, they were deliberately
OL,9,Faimed."
OL,11,FEarlier the trial heard that it was
OL,12,Fseemingly a "policy" of the accused to
OL,13,Fdestroy clothing they had been wearing.
OL,15,FIt came after a sequence of events,
OL,16,Fincluding rioting in the same area on
OL,17,FApril 16 and gatherings filmed by MTV,
OL,18,Ffrom which the clothing and features
OL,19,Fof those involved are contended to
OL,20,Fmatch those involved on April 18.
OL,26,@nD@aOUoD@QO]oD@\OUqD@GO]tD@MOUtD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1774548358
OL,3,COne of Lyra McKee murder accused 'part
OL,4,Cof shooting party'
OL,6,FHowever a number of items of clothing
OL,7,Fhave not been recovered, with the
OL,8,Fprosecution in the case contending it
OL,9,Fwas a "fact to bear in mind", and a
OL,10,F"policy" that clothes were destroyed.
OL,12,FThe non-trial opened in May 2024. In
OL,13,FFebruary, Judge Smyth rejected a
OL,14,Fdefence application that there was no
OL,15,Fcase to answer.
OL,17,FThe prosecution started their final
OL,18,Fsubmissions at Belfast Crown Court on
OL,19,FWednesday.
OL,26,@qD@GOUqD@\O]rD@AOUrD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1774548358
OL,3,COne of Lyra McKee murder accused 'part
OL,4,Cof shooting party'
OL,6,FThe defendants filled the dock
OL,7,Fwatching on as the prosecution summed
OL,8,Fup their case against them this week.
OL,10,FMs McKee's sister Nichola was among
OL,11,Fthose in the public gallery.
OL,13,FOn Wednesday, Mr McDowell KC said
OL,14,Fforensic image analyst Andrew Wooller
OL,15,Fidentified 19 individuals by height,
OL,16,Fbuild, clothing and trainers who
OL,17,Fappeared to be involved in the
OL,18,Fdisorder.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1774548358
OL,3,COne of Lyra McKee murder accused 'part
OL,4,Cof shooting party'
OL,6,FHe said Cavanagh, Devine and McIntyre,
OL,7,Fas well as Campbell and Gillen, can be
OL,8,Flinked to the scene on April 18 by an
OL,9,Fanalysis of imagery gathered, which
OL,10,Fincludes footage filmed by the MTV
OL,11,Fcrew on the day of the shooting in the
OL,12,FSaoradh office as well as during
OL,13,Frioting.
OL,15,FIt was contended that McIntyre played
OL,16,Fa "leading role", and was a person
OL,17,Fseen gathering up items from the
OL,18,Fground, believed to be cartridges from
OL,19,Fthe ground after the shooting.
OL,26,@xD@COUxD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44114
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1774548358
OL,3,COne of Lyra McKee murder accused 'part
OL,4,Cof shooting party'
OL,6,FMeanwhile, Devine had been described
OL,7,Fas having been seen wearing
OL,8,Fdistinctive trainers, tracksuit
OL,9,Fbottoms and a US Polo Association cap
OL,10,Fon a number of occasions, linking him
OL,11,Fwith person B from riot footage on
OL,12,FApril 18.
OL,14,FThe defence are set to make their
OL,15,Fclosing submissions next month.
